[[Translation:en/Community/NewGRF/Generic Road Vehicle and Tram Set]]
'''Generic Road Vehicle and Tram Set''' provides road vehicles and [[en/Manual/Tramways]] for all [[en/Manual/Climates]]s in dual [[en/Archive/Manual/Company Colours]], with articulated vehicles. This set uses [[en/Manual/Refit]]ting and generic cargo classes, so may be used with any [[en/Archive/Manual/NewGRF Industries|new industry set]] (although some cargos may use generic graphics).

[[File:en/Community/NewGRF/GRVTS preview 2.png|center]]

==Vehicles==

Buses:
*5x Normal
*4x Double-Decker
*3x Articulated (1 trailer)
*3x Express (coaches)

Heavy industry cargos (hopper, flatbed and tanker):
*4x Normal
*4x Articulated (1 trailer)

Light industry cargos (mail, box, armoured and refrigerated trucks):
*5x Normal
*3x Express

Passenger Trams:
*5x Normal (1, 2 or 3 car)
*3x Double decker (1 or 2 car)

Cargo trams (mail, goods, sweets and food only):
*4x Normal (1, 2, 3 or 4 car)

